Function Reference/timer start « WordPress Codex
-----------

PHP 5 standard microtime start capture.

Usage
-----

` <?php timer_start(  ); ?> `

Return Values
-------------

 `` `(boolean)`{style="color:gray"} 
:   Always returns true.

Change Log
----------

Since: [0.71](/Version_0.71 "Version 0.71")

Source File
-----------

`timer_start()` is located in `wp-includes/load.php`

